{"tid":119403,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男友送左禮物俾我 但我唔鍾意 應該點應對","createTime":"2017-02-13T17:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T14:45:46.000Z","uid":29111,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"607f4853eea309710dae3791f25605c6663d6916","tid":119403,"uid":29111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:02:57.000Z","msg":"我男友唔算好有潮流觸覺 我本人亦都唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今年情人節佢買左個無線藍牙耳機俾我 個人覺得都幾貴<br />\n但係個耳機太大舊 係男仔戴嗰d款 亦都唔係我style<br />\n我知你地會話我有禮物收仲嫌3嫌4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個款咁樣我又未必會用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁貴我唔用又驚佢唔開心<br />\n應該點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80721733fee006c4b25e246cb8000dc221c4031e","tid":119403,"uid":23590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:05:47.000Z","msg":"Trade咗佢"},{"pid":"c015175c4b4a0c61644273305f1f79089e2d5e17","tid":119403,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:06:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=2yJS3s3Gaa0&amp;sns=fb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2yJS3s3Gaa0%26sns%3Dfb&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=0d5dba32\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=2yJS3s3Gaa0&amp;sns=fb</a>"},{"pid":"1009c24b2e5ac1793e6cdaa7a779a7d00d0b0255","tid":119403,"uid":46246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:09:24.000Z","msg":"平平地幫你收左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f90c4d4bf36331433f688aa74a85da381d70c9","tid":119403,"uid":29111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Trade咗佢</blockquote><br />\n咁佢實知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4561e83751919e674a9cbbc7ef835339886c369","tid":119403,"uid":29111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:11:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平平地幫你收左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢實睇連登 我連個圖都唔敢放上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30263cfc4681115c2af738fc99e254e0de937c2a","tid":119403,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:13:17.000Z","msg":"係佢面前扮唔覺意跌爛"},{"pid":"d3c08d1be243aa3f771d6fccf38f80ffb3f53c26","tid":119403,"uid":83569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:13:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>平平地幫你收左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢實睇連登 我連個圖都唔敢放上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有幾多人會送呢樣俾女仔 準備俾bf起底啦你😎<br />\nbtw耳筒係咪J字頭個brand"},{"pid":"d125bb71986e54408aaa50d21752c3a0944779e9","tid":119403,"uid":29111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係佢面前扮唔覺意跌爛</blockquote><br />\n成千蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想俾返佢用架 但好賤格"},{"pid":"0d42dbb4c5ed618e5af578521cfe03eefce86563","tid":119403,"uid":29111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:18:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>平平地幫你收左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢實睇連登 我連個圖都唔敢放上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有幾多人會送呢樣俾女仔 準備俾bf起底啦你😎<br />\nbtw耳筒係咪J字頭個brand</blockquote><br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由佢起底啦 我唔想佢浪費金錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n寧願平 但真係鍾意"},{"pid":"f02fdae1630c04203f5755b068e136bee5135d44","tid":119403,"uid":6898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:23:42.000Z","msg":"佢自己本身鐘唔鐘意個禮物先?<br />\n通常男仔送d你唔岩洗既野俾你 多數佢本身好鐘意先想同你分享<br />\n你探下口風佢點睇份禮物先啦<br />\n如果佢自己好鐘意既不如你搵個機會叫佢買隻平d俾你換番隻貴野俾佢啦<br />\n咁等大家都有得用 不過你最好講明買d咩款<br />\n事關佢今次買錯 證明佢未知你心水係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"694dfce92b18f62ecdbba3e294e78ccfdad135d5","tid":119403,"uid":3287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:26:53.000Z","msg":"我諗佢本身自己鐘意先會送俾你 仲要咁貴<br />\n幾唔鐘意都係咁意出街喺佢面次戴幾次啦<br />\n怕柒咪搭巴士嗰陣戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5965de4037b47cb0961846e0a44d331fd276dd9c","tid":119403,"uid":78781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:31:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=2yJS3s3Gaa0&amp;sns=fb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2yJS3s3Gaa0%26sns%3Dfb&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=0d5dba32\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=2yJS3s3Gaa0&amp;sns=fb</a>&amp;sns=fb</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6c017ca4f488ca9124a34ff218f5cb94d5e9314","tid":119403,"uid":29111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:48:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢自己本身鐘唔鐘意個禮物先?<br />\n通常男仔送d你唔岩洗既野俾你 多數佢本身好鐘意先想同你分享<br />\n你探下口風佢點睇份禮物先啦<br />\n如果佢自己好鐘意既不如你搵個機會叫佢買隻平d俾你換番隻貴野俾佢啦<br />\n咁等大家都有得用 不過你最好講明買d咩款<br />\n事關佢今次買錯 證明佢未知你心水係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身有啲難揣摩點解佢會送俾我<br />\n但你又講得幾有道理 佢本身都鍾意份禮物奈何係我唔啱<br />\n我試下搵機會同佢講下 或者我同佢share用都得<br />\n費事浪費左份禮物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3edb47305360c01d4ceab28637bbd95aaede6983","tid":119403,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:48:04.000Z","msg":"出圖睇吓係咪真係無潮流觸覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e088b1e22cb370b751acc24099ff110f6bb2c145","tid":119403,"uid":39608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:49:58.000Z","msg":"屋企用囉"},{"pid":"332835cdef450e88da73ca2483ed3266ef73a44a","tid":119403,"uid":29111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:50:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我諗佢本身自己鐘意先會送俾你 仲要咁貴<br />\n幾唔鐘意都係咁意出街喺佢面次戴幾次啦<br />\n怕柒咪搭巴士嗰陣戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我送禮物俾佢都係送佢啱用+鍾意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都要學下由男仔角度出發諗嘢<br />\n一定會戴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930957a8ff7f9244df78c15fd72d4fbbd4445347","tid":119403,"uid":29111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:55:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出圖睇吓係咪真係無潮流觸覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/14/015350_deae1ec1168958a223febbfa98dd13b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F14%2F015350_deae1ec1168958a223febbfa98dd13b3.jpg&h=9ae6c039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男朋友我自爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 客觀討論 唔好嬲我 大家一齊用"},{"pid":"4fb250fcb0817fdd6c03f3f2ceeac4eccfcf6bf1","tid":119403,"uid":29111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T17:56:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企用囉</blockquote><br />\n都得嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373b65975dff52755b3a935a5014f4b1e4fa1fe2","tid":119403,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出圖睇吓係咪真係無潮流觸覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/14/015350_deae1ec1168958a223febbfa98dd13b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F14%2F015350_deae1ec1168958a223febbfa98dd13b3.jpg&h=9ae6c039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男朋友我自爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 客觀討論 唔好嬲我 大家一齊用</blockquote><br />\n柒到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加千蚊買個YSL card holder 好撚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好明顯係佢自己想要 但唔捨得買俾自己用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買電子野俾女仔既男朋友真係陣毒味重到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa68d557617372d4e3a2d4d87ba141247a0e6b30","tid":119403,"uid":6898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出圖睇吓係咪真係無潮流觸覺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/14/015350_deae1ec1168958a223febbfa98dd13b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F14%2F015350_deae1ec1168958a223febbfa98dd13b3.jpg&h=9ae6c039&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男朋友我自爆啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 客觀討論 唔好嬲我 大家一齊用</blockquote><br />\nOk啦 依家d藍牙耳機款係咁上下<br />\n不過係少見有女用家咁解"},{"pid":"150fd617a241e8473e8fd1f54a73c3d1dcabe0e3","tid":119403,"uid":3287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:11:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我諗佢本身自己鐘意先會送俾你 仲要咁貴<br />\n幾唔鐘意都係咁意出街喺佢面次戴幾次啦<br />\n怕柒咪搭巴士嗰陣戴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我送禮物俾佢都係送佢啱用+鍾意<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都要學下由男仔角度出發諗嘢<br />\n一定會戴下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n明嘅 女仔送會費盡心思<br />\n我嗰個要手作野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然真係好唔啱但禮貌上我覺得都要用吓<br />\n唯有有機會試吓透露吓對電子野無興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對野你試吓用幾次 之後借啲意叫佢袋住先<br />\n再話擺喺佢度先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b233c86bf5e5c2f820306220c4e00b20aca36654","tid":119403,"uid":10566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T18:34:37.000Z","msg":"你依樣都叫用得啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebadf6aea27f00393cb5b3449df9852702959bf1","tid":119403,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T21:35:18.000Z","msg":"其實佢係買比佢自己"},{"pid":"56a5e9fd7b65f4f69ef3ff71a728cf66372dff72","tid":119403,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:36:51.000Z","msg":"同佢坦白，但認真表明心意已領"}]}